OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1778080262
OL,3,CCandidate warned after using parish
OL,4,Cresources for re-election bid
OL,6,FThe current Constable of St Saviour
OL,7,Fhas been warned after using parish
OL,8,Fresources to promote his re-election
OL,9,Fbid.
OL,11,FKevin Lewis took advantage of his
OL,12,Faccess to the parish mailing list to
OL,13,Femail prospective voters, laying out
OL,14,Fhis achievements and candidacy for
OL,15,FJune's Jersey Election.
OL,17,FAn article was also posted on the
OL,18,Ffront of the parish website, which has
OL,19,Fsince been removed.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
