PN,38102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1778080262
OL,3,CCandidate warned after using parish
OL,4,Cresources for re-election bid
OL,6,FAnother candidate complained to the
OL,7,FJersey Electoral Authority, which has
OL,8,Fissued a letter to the Comite des
OL,9,FConnetables, "reminding its members
OL,10,Fthat parish resources should not be
OL,11,Fused for electoral purposes".
OL,13,FThe body, which provides independent
OL,14,Foversight of the island's elections,
OL,15,Fwill also ask the next government to
OL,16,Fissue guidance to all politicians
OL,17,Fahead of future polls.
OL,26,@pD@]rrqD@Err
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1778080262
OL,3,CCandidate warned after using parish
OL,4,Cresources for re-election bid
OL,6,FHowever, the Authority and Jersey's
OL,7,Fdata regulator rejected a claim that
OL,8,Fpersonal information had been misused
OL,9,Fas the campaign material was only
OL,10,Fshared with those who subscribed to
OL,11,Fthe St Saviour Parish mailing list.
OL,13,FMichael Marett-Crosby, the Chair of
OL,14,Fthe Jersey Electoral Authority,
OL,15,Fexplains: "The JEA is committed to
OL,16,Fdoing all within its power to ensure
OL,17,Fthat there is a level playing field
OL,18,Fbetween all candidates.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1778080262
OL,3,CCandidate warned after using parish
OL,4,Cresources for re-election bid
OL,6,F"This is essential if we wish to
OL,7,Fensure that our elections are fair and
OL,8,Ffollow best democratic practice.
OL,10,F"The JEA urges that all sitting
OL,11,Fmembers who are standing for election
OL,12,Frespect the important principle that
OL,13,Fparish and government resources should
OL,14,Fnot be used for electoral purposes."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/6
