OL,3,CCandidate warned after using parish
OL,4,Cresources for re-election bid
OL,6,FHe is standing in the election on
OL,7,FSunday 7 June against two other
OL,8,Fcandidates: Dave Curtis and Suzie Webb.
OL,10,FAll three are independent candidates
OL,11,Fand their manifestos can be found here
OL,12,Fon the official vote.je website.
